description:
Play through the first Touhou Project DLC for Sixtar Gate: STARTRAIL!
This DLC contains 11+1 new songs and a new original theme.

New Songs:
1. Satori the Witch - yomoha
2. 幻想のサテライト - 豚乙女
3. 悪戯センセーション - 森羅万象
4. 儚きもの人間 - 豚乙女
5. 全力ハッピーライフ- 森羅万象
6. 進め！イッスン軍団- yoa(dawn-system)
7. Shooting Star feat. Risa Yuzuki - uma vs. モリモリあつし
8. 患部で止まってすぐ溶ける～狂気の優曇華院 - IOSYS
9. VENTEN - 暁Records
10. Calamity Fortune – LeaF
11. *** **** ****** - y*****
EX. KARMANATIONS - 暁Records

Theme:
“Welcome to Gensokyo!”
This theme is exclusive to the Touhou Project 01 pack.
name: Sixtar Gate: STARTRAIL - Touhou Project Pack 01
